(1, 'PD-22-000001', 1, 5, NULL, 'DR Rashel Vitamin C Brightening & Anti Ageing Face Serum 50ml', '<p>Function: Whitening, Moisturizing, Anti Wrinkle Skin type: All Skin Types</p>', '<ul>\r\n	<li>New improved formula, DR&middot;RASHEL Vitamin C face Serum is thin and highly effective.</li>\r\n	<li>It will help fade sun spots &amp; discoloration, refine skin texture, reduce wrinkle formation, and minimize existing wrinkles.</li>\r\n	<li>It also has a high concentrated base of pure vegan hyaluronic acid to plump skin cells and protect and restore.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Brightens and smoothes skin for a more radiant and youthful complexion.</li>\r\n	<li>Powerful antioxidants neutralize free radicals to prevent and reverse sun damage and fade sun spots and discoloration.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;How to Use :&nbsp;</strong>Apply evenly to face and neck in the morning and evening then Massage in circular motions for better absorption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671459805981-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-anti-ageing-face-serum-50ml.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671459806844-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-anti-ageing-face-serum-50ml.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/167145980682-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-anti-ageing-face-serum-50ml.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/167145980612-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-anti-ageing-face-serum-50ml.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2000.00, 200.00, 10.00, 10.00, 10.00, 100.00, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-anti-ageing-face-serum-50ml', '2022-12-19 19:53:25', '2022-12-19 19:53:25'),
(2, 'PD-22-000002', 1, 5, NULL, 'DR Rashel Vitamin C Eye Serum Remove Dark Circles Eye Bags Anti-wrinkle', '<p>Features: Anti aging, freckle removal, moisturizing, brightening Skin Type: All skin types</p>', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Vitamin C eye serum deeply nourishes the delicate skin around the eyes, reduces wrinkles on the eyes, and brightens the eyes.</li>\r\n	<li>Contains pure vitamin C and collagen, known for its affinity with skin and its ability to improve the appearance of aging skin.</li>\r\n	<li>With hyaluronic acid, it strengthens, soothes and brightens the eye, helping to eliminate dark circles.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong>How to Use</strong> : Apply a Small Amount Of Eye Treatment With Fingertip Along The Orbital Bone And Under Eye Area. Pat Gently Without Pulling The Skin.</p>', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671459967435-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-eye-serum-remove-dark-circles-eye-bags-anti-wrinkle.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671459967332-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-eye-serum-remove-dark-circles-eye-bags-anti-wrinkle.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671459967279-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-eye-serum-remove-dark-circles-eye-bags-anti-wrinkle.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671459967605-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-eye-serum-remove-dark-circles-eye-bags-anti-wrinkle.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 2000.00, 200.00, 10.00, 10.00, 10.00, 100.00, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dr-rashel-vitamin-c-eye-serum-remove-dark-circles-eye-bags-anti-wrinkle', '2022-12-19 19:56:07', '2022-12-19 19:56:07'),
(4, 'PD-22-000003', 1, 5, NULL, 'Dr.Rashel Vitamin C Brightening and Anti-Aging Facial Cleanser 80g', '<p>DR RASHEL Vitamin C Facial Cleanser refreshes and restores skins natural vibrance and clarity with powerful Vitamin C. It boosts of antioxidants which repairs and protects skin from environmental damage and sun exposure. Protects skin from environmental damage and sun exposure. Helps fade sun spots and discoloration Refines skin texture Reduce wrinkles and fine lines Provides a youthful and whitening complexion Even out skin</p>', '<p><strong>Dr.Rashel&nbsp;Vitamin C&nbsp;Cleanser&nbsp;Brightening and Anti-Aging 80g&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Brand &ndash; DR.RASHEL</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Skin Type &ndash; All skin types</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Item Form &ndash; Facial cleanser</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Item Weight &ndash; 80g</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Description:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dr.Rashel Vitamin C Facial Cleanser refreshes and restores skin&rsquo;s natural vibrance and clarity with powerful Vitamin C. It boasts of antioxidants that repair and protect skin from environmental damage and sun exposure. Contains vitamin c and hyaluronic acid ingredients that help fade sun spots and discoloration, refine skin texture and reduce wrinkle. Gently remove impurities to reveal a more youthful and whitening complexion. Vitamin C in this cleanser is touted as one of the best anti-aging ingredients on the market &mdash; and the key to maintaining a smooth, even, and glowy complexion.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It also inhibits melanin production in the skin, which helps to lighten hyperpigmentation and brown spots, even out skin tone, and enhance skin radiance. Hyaluronic acid is well known for its skin benefits, especially alleviating dry skin, reducing the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles. In conclusion, DR.RASHEL Vitamin C Facial Cleanser is,</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Formulated with powerful ingredients to prevent sun damage &amp; fade sunspot.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;Formulated to help moisturize, nourish and protect dull, tired, aging skin.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;It supports skin&rsquo;s collagen and elastin and brightens the complexion.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;The serum delivers the natural actives into the skin and helps to nourish it.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Neutralizes skin damage that helps to avoid signs of skin aging.</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp; &nbsp;Also, even&rsquo;s out patchy complexion and minimizes pigmentation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Buy Dr.Rashel Vitamin C Brightening and Anti-Aging Facial Cleanser for the best price in Sri Lanka.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Benefits:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Protects skin from environmental damage and sun exposure.</li>\r\n	<li>Helps fade sun spots and discoloration</li>\r\n	<li>Refines skin texture</li>\r\n	<li>Reduce wrinkles and fine lines</li>\r\n	<li>Provides a youthful and whitening complexion</li>\r\n	<li>Even out skin</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>How to Use:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Firstly, Squeeze out a small coin-sized amount of Dr.Rashel Vitamin C Brightening and Anti-Aging Facial Cleanser on your palm.</li>\r\n	<li>Secondly, massage the foaming cleanser onto wet skin in circular motions.</li>\r\n	<li>Finally, rinse with water. Use at least twice a day for best results.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Key Ingredients:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vitamin C and Hyaluronic Acid</p>', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671460167847-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-facial-cleanser-80g.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671460167949-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-facial-cleanser-80g.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671460167651-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-facial-cleanser-80g.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671460167518-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-facial-cleanser-80g.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1750.00, 0.00, NULL, 10.00, 10.00, 100.00, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-facial-cleanser-80g', '2022-12-19 19:59:27', '2022-12-19 19:59:27'),
(5, 'PD-22-000004', 1, 5, NULL, 'Dr.Rashel Vitamin C Brightening and Anti-Aging Face Night Cream 50g', '<p>Effective, yet gentle face night cream packed with valuable ingredients is safe for all skin types. It has been formulated with a high concentration of Niacinamide and Vitamin C that provide daily hydration to the skin</p>', '<h2><strong>Dr.Rashel Vitamin Night Cream 50g</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Brand &ndash; Dr.Rashel<br />\r\nSkin Type &ndash; All skin types<br />\r\nItem Form &ndash; Night Cream<br />\r\nItem Weight &ndash; 50g</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Description:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Dr.Rashel Vitamin C<strong>&nbsp;Night Cream</strong>&nbsp;is a highly effective light gel that neutralizes skin damage. It is packed with antioxidants and ingredients that provide&nbsp;<strong>daily hydration to the skin</strong>. This night cream has been formulated with a high concentration of&nbsp;<strong>Niacinamide and Vitamin C</strong>&nbsp;that provide daily hydration to the skin. Above all this night cream absorb quickly to your skin and provide many anti-aging skin benefits. This Night Cream leave skin clarified to&nbsp;<strong>reveal radiant skin</strong>&nbsp;and a&nbsp;<strong>renewed complexion</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, this cream will help to&nbsp;<strong>fade sun spots, and discoloration</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>refine skin texture, reduce wrinkle formation and minimize existing wrinkles</strong>.<br />\r\nIn conclusion, this face night cream is,</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Formulated with potent ingredients to protect against sun damage and fade sunspots.</li>\r\n	<li>This night cream hydrates nourishes and protects dull, tired, aging skin.</li>\r\n	<li>It helps to support the skin&rsquo;s collagen and elastin while also brightening the complexion.</li>\r\n	<li>The cream also helps to nourish the skin by delivering natural actives into it.</li>\r\n	<li>This night cream will neutralize skin damage, which aids in the prevention of skin aging.</li>\r\n	<li>Evens out patchy skin and reduces pigmentation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>For youthful and wrinkle-free skin buy&nbsp;<strong>Dr.Rashel Vitamin C Brightening and Anti-Aging Face Night Cream from Cosmetics.lk</strong>&nbsp;for the best price Sri Lanka.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>How to Use:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>After cleansing and toning, apply a small amount of Dr. Rashel Vitamin C Brightening and Anti-Aging Face Night Cream. Massage to the face and neck until fully absorbed.</li>\r\n	<li>Apply Day Cream in the morning and Night Cream at night time.</li>\r\n	<li>Best used with Dr. Rashel Vitamin c serum. Use after a cleansed face, before makeup application.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3>Key Ingredients:</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Vitamin C, Niacinamide</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Also, the benefits of vitamin C are well known in the skincare industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Benefits of Vitamin C:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Provide many anti-aging skin benefits.</li>\r\n	<li>Minimizing the appearance of wrinkles.</li>\r\n	<li>Tightening and firming skin.</li>\r\n	<li>Brightening skin.</li>\r\n	<li>Eliminating skin blemishes.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671460235658-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-face-night-cream-50g.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/167146023545-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-face-night-cream-50g.png', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1671460235887-dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-face-night-cream-50g.png', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1750.00, 0.00, NULL, 10.00, 10.00, 50.00, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dr-rashel-vitamin-c-brightening-and-anti-aging-face-night-cream-50g', '2022-12-19 20:00:35', '2022-12-19 20:00:35'),
