(195, 'PD-22-000187', 10, 59, NULL, 'Bestway Steel pro Max Swimming Pool (10\'\'x30\'\')', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Size: 3.05 m x 76 cm (10 ft. x 30 in.)</li>\r\n	<li>Water Capacity (90%): 4,678 L (1,236 gal.)</li>\r\n	<li>1,249 L (330 gal.) filter pump included</li>\r\n	<li>Easy, no-tool setup and takedown process</li>\r\n	<li>Easy 20-minute setup</li>\r\n	<li>Corrosion resistant metal frames</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to dissemble when preparing for off-season storage</li>\r\n	<li>Heavy-duty PVC and polyester 3-ply side walls</li>\r\n	<li>3-ply band provides additional wall support</li>\r\n	<li>Printed mosaic inner liner on the sides and bottom of the pool</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><strong>Steel Pro Max.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easy to assembleDurable PVC and polyester with three-layer side wallsThe built-in drain valve can be connected to a garden hose with the included adapter to drain the water easily. Self-adhesive underwater repair patch3-layer stand protection for additional wall stability.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>305 cm x 76 cm</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The extra strong side walls of this pool are made of Tritech, a three-layer, reinforced material with polyester mesh core, which is incorporated into two high density PVC layers. Depending on the size of the pool, this creates a material thickness of 0.40-0.80 mm (16-32 gauge), which ensures exceptional strength and durability. Steel frame with corrosion protection coating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Water capacity: 4.678 L (1.236 gal.)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&quot;Seal &amp; Lock System&quot; steel frame connection system to protect against water entry into the poles. Mosaic print on the inside of the pool walls and the pool floor. Easy to dismantle and space-saving storage at the end of the season. The round shape is particularly easy to assemble, offers increased stability and requires hardly any additional space outside the pool.</p>', 'https://greenguardexpress.lk/uploads/products/1670613656841-bestway-steel-pro-max-swimming-pool-10-x30-.