(333, 'PD-22-000324', 2, 17, NULL, 'Paint Zoom Paint Sprayer Machine', '<ul>\r\n	<li>HANDY EXTENSION &amp; UNIQUE PAINT SPRAYER NOZZLE</li>\r\n	<li>FOR INDOOR &amp; OUTDOOR USE</li>\r\n	<li>FOR WALLS, CEILINGS &amp; ANY HOME PAINTING NEEDS</li>\r\n	<li>The Paint Zoom electric paint sprayer is an airbrush sprayer for home use.</li>\r\n	<li>This paint zoom delivers flawless results, allowing for efficient paint distribution and drying once the paint has been sprayed.</li>\r\n	<li>Our electric spray gun is compact and lightweight for easy transportation, maneuverability, and speed.</li>\r\n	<li>The Paint Zoom paint sprayer cuts the mess and hassle of painting your home in half.</li>\r\n	<li>While it is still recommended to use a drop cloth and tape in some areas, this sprayer tool is a must-have for anyone looking to repaint their home.</li>\r\n	<li>Unlike airless paint sprayers, or even other electric spray guns that can stutter or otherwise interrupt the even flow and distribution of paint, our Paint Zoom eliminates the risk of uneven coating.</li>\r\n	<li>This paint sprayer features a powerful motor and distributes an even coat of paint every time, so you get it right the first time.</li>\r\n	<li>Our convenient paint sprayer are designed for both indoor and outdoor use.</li>\r\n	<li>With its rugged, heavy-duty materials, these ruggedly durable spray can tackle any paint job, whether it&rsquo;s for your home&rsquo;s interior or a job outside the house.</li>\r\n	<li>With the Paint Zoom electric air paint sprayer, sprucing up your home with a new color theme is easier than ever.</li>\r\n	<li>This paint sprayer tool gives you maximum directional control with our unique reinforced three-way spray nozzle head.</li>\r\n	<li>Additionally, its long extension hose gives you even more freedom when it comes to your paint job, taking it to the max.</li>\r\n	<li>Say goodbye to rollers and brushes with our Paint Zoom Pro compressor painting machine</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 'https://g